condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Sch 2: Sect 1.B; para 6(c) | Description :The Borrower shall adopt a comprehensive multi-agency localdevelopment strategy. | Due Date :15-Dec-2011
Finance Agreement :Sch 2; Sect 1.B; para 6(b) | Description :The Borrower shall adopt new urban planning standards and guidelines.| Due Date :15-Mar-2013

Finance Agreement :Sch 2; Sect 1.B; para 7 | Description :Beginning the 2nd year of project implementation, and each yearthereafter of project duration, the Borrower shall prepare, publish& distribute a joint MOMA/MOF annual report subject to Bankapproval | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Sch 2; Sect 1.B; para 6(a) | Description :The Borrower shall prepare and adopt an equalization transfer systemsetting out inter-alia measures to ensure equitable distribution of resources amongst the municipalities. | Due Date :15-Dec-2011
